  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1076">
<l>aṟaipaṟai yaṉṉar kayavartāṅ kēṭṭa </l>
<l>maṟaipiṟark kuytturaitta lāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The base are like a drum that is beaten, for they unburden to others the secrets they have heard.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
